divs: Sighting DetailsFebruary of 2007 we were looking at pictures taken August 06, when we noticed a UFO in the upper right hand corner of the picture. Really was not an "event" in that we were unaware of the object at the time the picture was taken. 1.We were hiking on the mid-mountain trail between Pinebrook and The Canyons Resort in Park City, UT. 2.We did not notice the object until looking at pictures 6 months later. 3.We cannot identify the object. 4.Cannot describe object from picture but it is disc like with some sort of legs coming off. 5-6. We did not notice the object when the picture was taken.
Summary: Object seen in picture taken 6 months ago on a hiking trip in the Utah mountains.
trends: There have been 7 other sightings in Park City

This sighting has never been favorited.
